channel.title: Rename the RSC private server advertisement section
channel.description: Rename it to XML RSC Private servers and start a new section where only admins/mods/vets can move topics to called "RSC Private Servers". Might encourage the very few people here with the knowledge to change anything besides XML to actually start doing it.

item.description:
@xEnt wrote:

Completely wrong. It needs to be named

“Setting up RSC Servers, and other noobish shit” I’ve yet to see anyone do anything in a long time, or struggle for help that they actually did part of, and not requested shit.
